x;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;list-style-type:square;mso-special-format:bu=
llet"><li><i>Meyer=E2=80=99s bad bet</i>: As it turns out, <b>Ron Meyer</b>=
, the co-founder of Creative Artists Agency and the former longtime preside=
nt of Universal Studios, really does like to gamble. The Hollywood rainmake=
r, whose friends have <u><a href=3D"https://email.puck.news/e/c/eyJlbWFpbF9=
pZCI6ImRnVDJ4Z1lEQUt2UktxclJLZ0dSVXl4aFU5eUtfUXJqbGNHSk5MQT0iLCJocmVmIjoiaH=
R0cHM6Ly92YXJpZXR5LmNvbS8yMDIxL2ZpbG0vbmV3cy9qb2VsLXNpbHZlci1yb24tbWV5ZXItZ=
2FtYmxpbmctZGVidC1uYmN1bml2ZXJzYWwtMTIzNDg5NzU0NC8_dXRtX2NhbXBhaWduPURyeStQ=
b3dkZXIrLStTVUJTQ1JJQkVSUyslMjg4JTJGMTQlMkYyNCUyOVx1MDAyNnV0bV9jb250ZW50PUR=
yeStQb3dkZXIrLStTVUJTQ1JJQkVSUyslMjg3JTJGMjQlMkYyNCUyOVx1MDAyNnV0bV9tZWRpdW=
