126e4fcb60126a8c1b36532" style=3D"color:#d40000;text-decoration:none;font-w=
eight:bold" class=3D"sdf">reported</a></u> on Monday, there is also a growi=
ng frustration <i>inside</i> WBD, where Zaz has been likened by some to Mic=
hael Scott, <b>Steve Carell</b>=E2=80=99s comic boob of a manager from <i>T=
he Office</i>. <br/><br/>Clearly, Zaz <i>et al.</i> are still absorbing the=
 fallout from WBD=E2=80=99s brutal second-quarter performance that I wrote =
